	<text>
		<body>
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002079_0001"><!--pb/@n='82r'--></pb>
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Newstead Abbey</placeName>
<lb/><placeName><settlement type="town">Mansfield</settlement></placeName>, <placeName><region><choice><abbr>Notts.</abbr><expan>Nottinghamshire</expan></choice></region></placeName><!-- First two lines are type-written header for stationery HB 9/25/12 -->
<lb/><date when="1864-10-01">1<hi rend="sup">st</hi> <choice><abbr>Oct<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi></abbr><expan>October</expan></choice> 1864</date></p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>Waller</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I return the
<lb/>photographs &amp; lots of
<lb/>sympathy for your
<lb/>loss.- I told <persName>Miss
<lb/>Watson</persName> that I would
<lb/>ask you for the
<lb/><choice><abbr>photos.</abbr><expan>photographs</expan></choice> of the <orgName>black
<lb/>people</orgName> - so they will
<lb/>go only from you
<lb/>I shall add again
<lb/>that they are from
<lb/><persName><choice><abbr>H.</abbr><expan>Horace</expan></choice> Waller</persName> so keep

        

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002079_0002"><!--pb/@n='82v'--></pb>
<lb/>up your heart - only
<lb/>a nice <term type="nationality">Scotch</term> girl
<lb/>like her cannot afford
<lb/>to <del type="cancelled">a</del> stoop to a man
<lb/>who snores ingloriously
<lb/>while being robbed.
<lb/>I supposed you were
<lb/>snoring the tune
<lb/>"man wants but little
<lb/>here below, nor wants
<lb/>that little long." <w>aoor<supplied>-</supplied><lb break="no"/>rrrrghroooaooog</w>
<lb/>Well done my man
<lb/>Why <choice><sic>dont</sic><corr>don't</corr></choice> you take
<lb/><persName>Jessie <unclear cert="medium">Lennox</unclear></persName> to tak<supplied cert="high">e</supplied>
<lb/>care of you. When

        

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002079_0003"><!--pb/@n='83r'--></pb>
<lb/>we were robbed
<lb/>on <placeName><geogName type="lake">Lake Nyasa</geogName></placeName>
<lb/>We felt awfully
<lb/>foolish - I am rejoicing
<lb/>in the belief that
<lb/>you are feeling
<lb/>the same - ! <persName>Miss
<lb/><choice><abbr> L.</abbr><expan cert="medium">Lennox</expan></choice></persName> is well - and

        

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002079_0004"><!--pb/@n='83v'--></pb>
<lb/><persName>Tozer</persName> by <persName>Jos√© Nunes</persName>
<lb/>Take it please at your
<lb/><choice><sic>leizure</sic><corr>leisure</corr></choice> to <unclear>mitre</unclear> court
<lb/>and ask if <add place="below">^</add> <add place="above">they</add> paid it to
<lb/><persName>George Thornton</persName> then
<lb/>tell me in a note with
<lb/>that alone as the subject
<lb/>that's what I get by
<lb/>saving his brothers</p><!-- Bleedthrough from previous page's verso HB 9/25/12 -->
			
</div>
